Acme-Thoroughly-Modern-Perl version v0.4.1
=========================

Release date: April 1, 2014

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

If you are on a windows box you should use 'nmake' rather than 'make'.

